sets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地要真正BE WATER!!!!<br />\nBe Water唔L係叫你走佬呀！！！<br />\n係要快閃！<br />\n每去一處地方撚完就要快閃，唔好留，再去另一度。要d狗去到又搵唔到任何手足，激L死！<br />\n然後佢地又要接order去第二度，吹到啤！<br />\n狗就係狗，要接order做，冇order就唔L識做，on99唔知點L算。<br />\n喺佢地未接到order時，我地已經喺另一度撚緊，可以撚L哂各區狗舍，狗屋。<br />\n班坐office嘅膠層就係調兵遣將嗰d，佢地會將新界嘅調出九龍，九龍西又調落尖沙咀等等⋯⋯佢地以為自己係軍師，但如果我地真正BE WATER，兵貴神速！佢地嘅智商一定會err...err...err....然後亂L哂！繼而自亂陣腳，內鬥⋯⋯真係諗下都開心！想下都興奮！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁樣，除咗可以減低手足被捕嘅機會，重可以減低「臥底」扮手足周圍抹黑嘅機會，因為佢地唔L知我地會去邊，佢地未部署係唔會識行動嘅！不過當然好大可能已經混入咗，跟住一齊去（啱啱喺學堂出嚟嗰d），但就大大削弱佢地嘅機動性！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家都有眼睇班狗毫無人性！見人就兇，見記者就推！都唔知幾多落單女女出事！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地要撚狗撚得醒d！快過d狗！唔好再玩雞蛋撞高牆！太多唔值得嘅白白犧牲！勇武好寶貴！不能再失！<br />\n而家和理非喺街度屌d狗都拉！記者俾狗打，俾狗推到老練咁遠根本乜都影唔到！<br />\n！係時候轉撚狗方法！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n1<br />\n0"},{"pid":"37767db4fde7e1b968165d4ba979ab267b444bfc","tid":1636092,"uid":17289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T17:28:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gpZRnja.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbna